[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0574","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0574.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0809","title":"Netscape Communicator Cookie 安全策略绕过漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 4.x 版本存在安全绕过漏洞。当用户启用 JavaScript 且已选择\"仅接受来自正浏览页面同一服务器之 Cookie\"选项时，浏览器仍不会对 Cookie 设置行为发出警告。攻击者可利用恶意网页绕过 Cookie 同源策略，跨站设置或窃取用户 Cookie，导致用户隐私泄露或会话劫持。漏洞影响 Netscape Communicator 4.x 全系版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0809"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.117","remediation":"停止使用 Netscape Communicator 4.x，升级至 Mozilla Firefox 或其它现代浏览器，并在浏览器设置中禁用 JavaScript 作为临时缓解措施。对于仍必须使用 Netscape 的场景，可在浏览器首选项中关闭 JavaScript 功能（Edit → Preferences → Advanced → Scripts & Plugins → 取消启用 JavaScript）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0809"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0574.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0453","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0453.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0752","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server SSL Handshake 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 3.6 及更早版本在处理 SSL 握手过程中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 SSL 握手请求触发该漏洞，导致服务器进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Netscape Enterprise Server 3.6 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。厂商已停止支持该产品，建议用户迁移至其他受支持的 Web 服务器。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0752"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:58.993","remediation":"Netscape Enterprise Server 已于 2000 年代停止维护，官方不再提供安全更新。建议立即迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server、Nginx 或 IIS），并禁用旧版 SSL/TLS 协议。临时缓解措施可在网络防火墙或反向代理层面过滤畸形 SSL 握手请求，限制源 IP 访问范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0752","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19416","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1231f6f5f21cc87f3264c90adadd01cbb12e76ba/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0752.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0752","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0752.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/77fd3cf167afc5c82646a191836bcd2f9e51b459/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0752.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jq89-jcvx-x6h9/GHSA-jq89-jcvx-x6h9.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0752.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--e6bc36b6-8003-41ad-8193-439e990880f9.json","https://github.com/michael1981/sfish_pt/blob/14f609d56e35e9810a1de14712293ab47cc03a46/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%2B%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F%2B%E7%88%86%E7%A0%B4/X-Scan-v3.3/plugins/netscape_crash.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0453.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0509","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0509.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0728","title":"Microsoft Windows NT IOCTL 调用权限许可和访问控制漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统中存在权限控制缺陷，本地用户可通过直接调用控制键盘和鼠标的 IOCTL 设备控制码来禁用这些输入设备，导致系统无法正常操作。该漏洞源于系统未对 IOCTL 调用进行充分的权限检查，允许低权限用户绕过访问控制。攻击者只需拥有本地登录权限即可利用此漏洞，影响 Windows NT 系列系统，CVSS 评分 7.8，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0728"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.960","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 或后续安全更新，限制非管理员用户对设备 IOCTL 的调用权限。对于已停止支持的旧系统，建议升级至 Windows Server 2016 或更高版本以彻底修复此漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ236359","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-024","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7638326ff3f30ccdb52a67547408dd61f5cdc6cc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0728.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0728","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0728.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0728.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r7mg-fmm2-chj3/GHSA-r7mg-fmm2-chj3.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0728.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0509.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1127","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1127.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1478","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 Sun Java HotSpot 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sun HotSpot Performance Engine VM 存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向运行 HotSpot 的服务器发送包含 \"[\" 字符的特制 URL 触发该漏洞，导致 Java 虚拟机崩溃并造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Microsoft IIS 4.0 等集成 Sun Java HotSpot 的 Web 服务器平台，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。攻击者只需构造简单的恶意 URL 即可实施攻击，无需其他前置条件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1478"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-06","updated":"1999-07-06","remediation":"升级至 Microsoft IIS 5.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，卸载 Sun Java HotSpot Performance Engine 或禁用 IIS 对 Java 的调用。在 IIS 中配置 URL 过滤规则，拦截包含非法字符（如 `[`）的请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/58a0ea900decdd7e971b95fcaa99234de5a5df5e/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1478.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1478","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1478.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/dabf5b9888e8885cf125c5729901a7ad84d00092/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1478.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-chqh-vf5r-qvxr/GHSA-chqh-vf5r-qvxr.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/1xxx/cve-1999-1478.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1478.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--44b1a868-b5e3-4dd6-8a6e-aa90eec10ca0.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1127.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1127.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1127.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1306","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1306.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0918","title":"Microsoft Windows IGMP 报文处理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 95/98/NT 3.51/NT 4.0/2000 的 IGMP 协议实现存在输入验证缺陷（CWE-20），远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的分片 IGMP 数据包，触发协议栈解析异常，导致目标系统蓝屏崩溃或服务完全停止。该漏洞无需用户交互即可远程触发，影响所有受支持的 Windows 9x/NT 系列版本，攻击者只需发送少量畸形数据包即可造成拒绝服务。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0918"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:19.657","remediation":"Windows 95/98 用户请通过 Microsoft Windows Update 安装安全更新或下载 MS99-034 补丁（KB Q238329）；Windows NT 4.0 用户请安装 Service Pack 6a 及后续安全汇总。上述系统均已终止支持，建议升级至 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 2016 以上版本。临时缓解措施：在边界防火墙上禁用 IGMP 协议或过滤碎片化 IGMP 报文。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ238329","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/514","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-034","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19415"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1306.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1097","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1097.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1394","title":"BSD 系列操作系统 UFS 安全级别绕过漏洞","description":"基于 BSD 4.4 的类 Unix 操作系统（包括 BSDI BSD/OS 4.0、FreeBSD 3.2、NetBSD 1.4 及 OpenBSD 2.5）在安全级别 1 模式下存在安全机制绕过漏洞。当系统运行于安全级别 1 时，具有 root 权限的攻击者可通过卸载文件系统，然后使用 fsdb 等文件系统编辑器直接操作底层设备，从而清除文件上设置的不可变（immutable）和仅追加（append-only）标志位。该漏洞破坏了安全级别机制对关键文件保护的设计意图，使得本应受保护的系统文件（如日志、审计记录等）可被恶意篡改。攻击者需要拥有 root 权限并具备文件系统卸载和底层设备操作能力，属于本地利用场景，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1394"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:20.763","remediation":"将系统安全级别提升至 securelevel 2（在 /etc/rc.conf 设置 kern_securelevel=2），该级别禁止写入原始磁盘设备，从而阻止通过 fsdb 等工具绕过不可变/仅追加标志。如无法提升安全级别，应避免向不可信用户授予 root 权限，并监控对 /dev 下原始磁盘设备的异常访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93094058620450&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/510","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19411","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1394.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1394","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1394.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1394.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-f7wg-pwf9-wgf9/GHSA-f7wg-pwf9-wgf9.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/510/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1394.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000688.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/adbddaf2c5b813c075c37b173049116b93b76066/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1097.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0248","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0248.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0688","title":"HP 软件分发器 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"HP-UX 系统的软件分发器（Software Distributor，简称 SD）在 10.x 与 11.x 版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该漏洞源于 SD 组件在处理特定输入时未对数据长度做充分边界校验，导致攻击者可控的过长数据写入固定大小的缓冲区，进而可覆盖相邻内存并可能实现任意代码执行。影响范围为运行 HPUX 10.x 和 11.x 且启用 SD 服务的系统。攻击条件为攻击者需能够向目标系统的 SD 服务发送特制请求，通常需要一定的本地或相邻网络访问权限。利用方式为构造恶意输入触发缓冲区溢出，造成服务异常或提升权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0688"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.047","remediation":"立即安装 HP-UX 11.11 或更高版本的 HP Software Distributor 补丁 HPD4365-11，或者应用 HPSBUX9907-101 安全更新。如需继续使用 HPUX 10.x，请应用 HP SD 10.20 补丁套件。立即更新系统，关闭不必要的 SD 服务以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/545","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9907-101","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0688.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0688","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0688.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0688.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-873q-3c4x-555r/GHSA-873q-3c4x-555r.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0688.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--9b15c9ce-60ad-4d9f-bb76-76ab2ab118a8.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0248.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0254","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0254.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0690","title":"HP CDE 将当前目录加入 root 的 PATH 环境变量导致权限提升漏洞","description":"HP CDE（Common Desktop Environment）在设置 root 用户环境变量 PATH 时错误地将当前目录 \".\" 包含在内，导致本地攻击者可在任意目录中放置与系统命令同名的恶意程序，当 root 用户通过 su 或登录进入该目录并执行未指定路径的命令时，恶意程序将以 root 权限自动执行，实现本地提权。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 系统中运行 CDE 的版本，需要攻击者拥有本地 shell 访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0690"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.300","remediation":"编辑 root 用户的 .profile、.login 或 CDE 系统级配置文件 /etc/dt/config/Xsession.d/ 下的相关脚本，移除 PATH 中的当前目录（即删除 \".\" 或空路径项），确保 PATH 仅包含绝对路径的系统目录（如 /usr/bin:/usr/sbin）。同时建议修改 CDE 启动脚本中 PATH 的拼接方式，使用完整路径调用命令，消除当前目录隐式搜索带来的提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-053.shtml","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9907-100","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0690.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0690","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0690.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0690.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rf75-mr45-vgcx/GHSA-rf75-mr45-vgcx.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_300_400.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0690.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-427.txt","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/CWE-Expert/blob/f634e911e6c24a1ad8b9619383e2ab3eb2d9ebd4/CWE_corpus/markdown/4_cwe_trimmed_top25.md.txt","https://github.com/ws-researcher/CAEA/blob/098ddb07c83845feda3d1b1d56ef634927954af4/KGA/dataSet/ICNS/entN_ids_1"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0254.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0296","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0296.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0707","title":"HP Visualize Conference FTP 未授权文件传输漏洞","description":"HP Visualize Conference 的默认 FTP 配置存在授权缺失漏洞。该软件在 HP-UX 系统上运行时，其 FTP 服务默认允许会议中的任意参与者向其他与会者发送文件，而无需经过任何身份验证或授权检查。远程攻击者可在未授权的情况下，利用该默认配置向会议中的其他用户传输任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露或恶意文件分发。该漏洞影响 HP Visualize Conference 相关版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0707"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:53.430","remediation":"立即应用 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9906-099 提供的补丁，或升级 HP Visualize Conference 至修复版本。如无法升级，在 FTP 服务配置中禁用未经授权的文件传输功能，并在网络层面限制对 FTP 端口（默认 21）的访问，仅允许受信任的 IP 连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-050.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/493","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9906-099","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6df16fc0c02ccadd2d0fbb0029e3db345d75f1c8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0707.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0707","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0707.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0707.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-c7p7-q447-5vcr/GHSA-c7p7-q447-5vcr.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0707.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000686.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0296.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0681","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0681.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0889","title":"Cisco 675路由器远程登录会话漏洞","description":"Cisco 675 路由器运行 CBOS 操作系统时存在未授权访问漏洞。如果管理员未设置 exec 或 superuser 密码，远程攻击者可通过 Telnet 协议直接建立登录会话，获得路由器的完全管理控制权限。攻击者无需任何认证即可访问设备，进而可能修改网络配置、窃取传输数据或发起进一步攻击。该漏洞影响 Cisco 675 系列路由器，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议管理员立即设置强密码或升级固件以修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0889"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:16.070","remediation":"立即为 Cisco 675 路由器设置 exec 和 superuser 密码（通过 `set password` 和 `set superuser-password` 命令），并配置访问控制列表限制 telnet 源 IP。建议升级到 CBOS 最新版本或更换支持 SSH 的现代设备，同时禁用非必要的 telnet 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/39"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0681.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0308","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0308.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0696","title":"CDE 日历管理器守护进程 rpc.cmsd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"CDE Calendar Manager Service Daemon（rpc.cmsd）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该服务在 Sun Solaris、HP-UX、Caldera OpenUnix 和 UnixWare 等系统上以 root 权限运行并监听 RPC 请求。攻击者可通过向 rpc.cmsd 发送超长格式的 RPC 请求触发缓冲区溢出，从而在目标系统上执行任意代码或导致服务拒绝服务。该漏洞影响网络可达且运行受影响的 Unix 操作系统的服务器和工作站。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0696"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1999-07-01","updated":"1999-07-01","remediation":"安装厂商发布的安全补丁或升级到修复后的系统版本。Sun 系统可参考 Sun Security Bulletin #188 获取补丁；HP-UX 系统应安装 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9908-102 对应的补丁；也可通过禁用 CDE 日历管理器服务（rpc.cmsd）来缓解该漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/188","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-051.shtml","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9908-102"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0308.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0004","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0004.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0140","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 RAS/PPTP 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 3.51 及 NT 4.0 的远程访问服务（RAS）与 PPTP 协议实现中存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标系统发送特制的畸形控制数据包，可导致 RAS/PPTP 服务崩溃或停止响应，造成系统无法正常提供远程访问功能。该漏洞无需用户交互即可远程触发，影响范围涉及企业远程接入环境，可能导致业务中断。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0140"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-06-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:40.957","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 或更高版本以修复 RAS/PPTP 协议处理中的缺陷。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022），并在防火墙上限制对 PPTP 端口（TCP 1723）的访问以降低暴露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0140","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20508","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0140.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0140","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0140.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0140.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0140.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fg49-hp4g-2h7r/GHSA-fg49-hp4g-2h7r.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/winnt_pptp_dos.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0140.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0004.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1065","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1065.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1348","title":"Red Hat Linux Linuxconf 本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 6.0 及更早版本中的 Linuxconf 工具未能正确禁用基于 PAM 的 shutdown 命令访问权限，导致本地用户可利用该缺陷直接执行 shutdown 命令，造成系统拒绝服务。该漏洞攻击条件低，本地用户无需特殊权限即可触发，影响 Red Hat Linux 6.0 及之前版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1348"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:14.943","remediation":"升级到 Red Hat Linux 6.1 或更高版本，该版本已修复 Linuxconf 对 shutdown 命令的 PAM 访问控制问题。如无法升级，可手动编辑 /etc/pam.d/shutdown 配置文件，移除或注释掉不必要的认证规则，限制仅 root 用户可执行 shutdown 命令。作为临时缓解措施，可通过 chmod 700 /sbin/shutdown 限制 shutdown 二进制文件的执行权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93220073515880&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7638326ff3f30ccdb52a67547408dd61f5cdc6cc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1348.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1348","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1348.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1348.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vfvh-4q9r-qw3j/GHSA-vfvh-4q9r-qw3j.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1348.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000685.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ee9754343b23d8c0f998865ae48a5d400d72ba81/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1065.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0508","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0508.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0726","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 畸形文件映像头拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 系统对可执行文件映像头的验证存在输入验证不足漏洞（CWE-20）。本地攻击者可通过执行特制的恶意程序，利用畸形的文件映像头触发系统异常，导致目标系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 版本，攻击者需具备本地执行权限，无法远程利用，但成功利用后可使系统崩溃或服务不可用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0726"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1999-06-30","updated":"2003-03-10","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 5 或单独安装 MS99-023 安全补丁。Windows NT Server 4.0、Windows NT Workstation 4.0 及 Windows NT Server 4.0 Terminal Server Edition 均受此漏洞影响，建议升级至 Service Pack 5 以彻底修复。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-023","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/499"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0508.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0715","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0715.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0916","title":"WebTrends 账户口令文件权限许可漏洞","description":"WebTrends 软件在安装目录中以明文文件存储账户名和密码，且该文件未设置充分的访问权限限制，导致本地攻击者可通过读取该文件获取敏感凭据信息。攻击者获得凭据后可进一步利用其他服务或系统资源，造成信息泄露。该漏洞影响 WebTrends 多个版本，利用条件为攻击者需具备本地文件系统访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0916"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:19.420","remediation":"将存储用户名和密码的文件（如 web.ini、wtlogin.txt）的 NTFS 权限设置为仅 SYSTEM 和管理员可读取，移除 Everyone 和 Users 组的访问权限；升级 WebTrends 到最新受支持版本；启用 Windows 集成身份验证或加密存储方式替代明文密码文件；定期审计关键文件的 ACL 配置。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0916"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0715.toml"}]